page.html:
Welcome to my osu profile page =)

Hello I'm KagaNyan (formerly chesterchek, its dumb to put real name as nick so I changed it), used to play a lot of VSRG such as O2Jam and DJMAX (yep, from Online until Trilogy & Portable 3).
A huge fan of Bemani series of music games since years.. too bad my country has very limited support of eAmusement (only Jubeat was brought in recent years.. and sdvx very recently yayy)
Used to be very active in osu! during year 2012-2013.. with only mouse and keyboard.
Started osumania at April 2015, but not very active tho bcoz of busy working life as indie game programmer/developer.

Update Sept 2016: Moved to SG for new career and entering completely darkness of bemani. bye osu.

SUCH MANY LEGIT PLAYERS IN MY COUNTRY.. MUCH WOW....


Currently not active in osu for some moments because of...

And this..
